content:
Optimize agent productivity and efficiently grow your knowledge base with AI-generated article drafts. Based on a customer conversation, Einstein drafts fluent, relevant knowledge articles that agents review, edit, and save.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on

To get started with Knowledge Creation, learn how to identify the right Knowledge fields for each Knowledge record type. Next, review the response type glossary, and see an example of Knowledge Creation in action.

Check the prerequisites, turn on article creation, and map your Knowledge record fields. Then, see how agents use Knowledge Creation in the console to draft and save articles. To get responses based on case details, add Case grounding to Knowledge Creation.

You can draft a knowledge article via a quick action on the Case page or from the Knowledge component. Edit and save your new article, and then submit it for approval and publishing.
title: Einstein Knowledge Creation in Service Cloud
